data.description: BACK ON MARKET AT NO FAULT TO THE SELLER! Welcome to 10906 Gold Pan Road where the appeal begins before entering! This home graciously provides 3 bedrooms, 2 and a half bathrooms, and a spacious bonus room. Upon entry, you are welcomed by a classic, neutral design with laminate flooring and carpet that flows throughout. The primary bedroom and en-suite, as well as the laundry room, are conveniently located on the main floor. The formal dining room, kitchen, breakfast dining area, and living room all serve as great hosting spaces for family gatherings. Upstairs, you'll find two additional bedrooms, 1 full bath, and a bonus room with endless opportunity. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home!
